		<td colspan="7" align="top" class="Content">The communications network employed by the Fire District to mobilize the third largest fire department in the state of Missouri is rather extensive and very unique.  The organization is dispatched by the Columbia/ Boone County Joint Communications Center, a communications center servicing all emergency services in Boone County.
